reviewText: My grandson loves Caillou. He couldn't wait to watch the new DVD..

This DVD contains seven episodes from the Caillou cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Dog Dilemma
2. Caillou's Cricket
3. Caillou's Cross Hop
4. Kitty Conundrum
5. Lost 'n' Found
6. Play with Me!
7. Caillou Roars
